$ Excel: Status bar
@ Status bar

Options that might be displayed in the status bar:
table { ll
  Cell mode ☰ *Ready*, *Enter*, *Edit* or *Point*.
  Flash fill blank/changed cells ☰ Number of → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Range/cell[cells] that were left empty/filled by a *flash fill*. Compare with `→ Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Range[range].autofill`.
  Signatures ☰ See also → Microsoft/Office/Excel/GUI/Ribbon/tabs/Insert/Text/Signature-Line[Insert -> Text -> Signature Line]
  Information management policy ☰
  Permissions ☰
  Caps Lock, Num Lock, Scroll Lock ☰
  Fixed decimal ☰
  Overtype mode ☰
  End mode ☰
  Macro recording ☰ Clicking this icon starts recording a macro. Compare with menu → Microsoft/Office/GUI/Ribbon/tabs/Developer/Code/Record-Macro[Developer -> Code -> Record Macro].
  Selection mode ☰
  Page number  ☰
  Average/count/numerical count/minimum/maximum//sum ☰ Numerical count, minimum and maximum are not shown by default.
  Upload status ☰
  View shortcuts ☰

table }

sa:

  `→ Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Application[application].statusBar `
